> So I think just use the `shuffle hint` is enough? No need to add new config `HASH_TBL_SPACE_OVERHEAD` or disallow broadcast large than 100MB?

I think we can set ```partition join``` as default  when we're unable to estimate the cost accurately and broadcast join cost equals partition join cost and without user hint.
From
```
                && broadcastCost <= partitionCost))) {
